  <brief_title>Use-Results Surveillance Study of Sovaldi® Plus Copegus® in Japanese Patients With Chronic Genotype 2 Hepatitis C Virus Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Observational Post-Marketing Study of Sovaldi® Plus Copegus® in Japanese Patients With Chronic Genotype 2 Hepatitis C Virus Infection</official_title>
